Class DateAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • smile.data.Attribute
      • smile.data.DateAttribute

  • public class DateAttribute
extends Attribute
    Data attribute. The default format string accepts the ISO-8601 combined date and time format: "yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss".
